title: Backyard Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Ovo, Organic, Raw, Western, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Western-style cafe opened March 2015 with an extensive menu focusing on healthy food and drinks. Labels if gluten free, raw or vegan suitable. Many vegan desserts. Sample items include a superfood burger (vegan), ginger and turmeric tea and raw acai, goji and lavender cake.
